    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="octopress-web">Octopress Web</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Home: <a href="http://octopress.org/">http://octopress.org/</a></li>
  <li>Document: <a href="http://octopress.org/docs/">http://octopress.org/docs/</a></li>
